            <p>
                I am Isaac Robb, the Director of Second Chance Mana PTY LTD. My mission is to empower individuals of all ages, particularly young people with disabilities, to develop practical life skills that enhance their independence, confidence, and social interaction. At Second Chance Mana, we offer a range of personalized services, including physical fitness training, tool usage, vehicle maintenance, first aid certification, fire safety, outdoor and survival skills, and more.
            </p>
